<link rel="stylesheet" href="/elements/index.css" />
<body>
	 <%- include("../modals/loginModal.ejs")
	%> <%- include("../modals/signUpModal.ejs") %>
	<!-- continue the frontEnd here  -->
	<header>
		<div class="box"></div>
		<nav>
			<ul class="navigate">
				<li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
				<li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
				<li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
			</ul>
		</nav>

		<div class="headerContent">
			<img src="/images/logo.png" alt="logo" class="logo" />

			<div class="btncontainer">
				<button
					class="button"
					type="button"
					data-bs-toggle="modal"
					data-bs-target="#loginModal"
				>
					Login
				</button>
				<button
					class="button"
					type="button"
					data-bs-toggle="modal"
					data-bs-target="#signUpModal"
				>
					Sign Up
				</button>
			</div>
			<h1>The Meal Bridge</h1>
			<div id="tagline-container"></div>
		</div>
	</header>
	<main>
		<section class="secc1">
			<div style="text-align: center">
				<h2>Who We Are?</h2>
			</div>
			<div style="text-align: center">
				 
				<p>The Meal Bridge is a platform designed to connect generous donors </p>
				<p> with food banks, community organizations, and those in need.</p>
				<p>Our mission is to bridge the gap between resources and recipients,</p>
				<p> ensuring that every donation reaches</p>
				<p>the right hands efficiently.</p>
			</div>
			<div style="text-align: center">
				<img src="/images/logo.png" alt="logo" class="logo" />
			</div>
		</section>
		<div style="text-align: center">
			<h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
		</div>
		<section>
			<div class="secc2">
				<div class="widget" onclick="toggleWidget(this)">
					<div class="questions">
						<button class="expand-btn">What is MealBridge?</button>
						<img src="/images/plus.svg" alt="imf" class="toggleimg" />
					</div>

					<div class="content">
						<p> The Meal Bridge is a platform that connects donors with food banks and community organizations, ensuring that food donations reach those in need efficiently and effectively.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="widget" onclick="toggleWidget(this)">
					<div class="questions">
						<button class="expand-btn">How does The Meal Bridge work?</button>
						<img src="/images/plus.svg" alt="img" class="toggleimg" />
					</div>

					<div class="content">
						<p> Donors contribute food, funds, or resources, which are then distributed to food banks or local organizations that support individuals and families facing food insecurity. Our platform facilitates a seamless connection between donors and these organizations to make the process efficient and impactful.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="widget" onclick="toggleWidget(this)">
					<div class="questions">
						<button class="expand-btn"> Who can donate through The Meal Bridge?</button>
						<img src="/images/plus.svg" alt="img" class="toggleimg" />
					</div>

					<div class="content">
						<p> Anyone! Whether you’re an individual, a family, a business, or an organization, you can contribute food, funds, or other resources to help those in need.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="widget" onclick="toggleWidget(this)">
					<div class="questions">
						<button class="expand-btn"> Can I choose which organization my donation goes to?</button>
						<img src="/images/plus.svg" alt="img" class="toggleimg" />
					</div>

					<div class="content">
						<p>Yes, our platform allows you to select specific food banks or organizations to support. Alternatively, you can let us allocate your donation to where it’s most needed</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="widget" onclick="toggleWidget(this)">
					<div class="questions">
						<button class="expand-btn"> How do I know my donation is making a difference?</button>
						<img src="/images/plus.svg" alt="img" class="toggleimg" />
					</div>

					<div class="content">
						<p> The Meal Bridge ensures transparency by partnering with trusted food banks and organizations. You’ll receive updates or confirmations detailing how your contributions have been used to make an impact.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="secc3">
			<h2>Stay connected</h2>
			<p>Sign up to receive news and updates about The Meal</p>
			<p>Bridge</p>
			<div class="btncontainer">
				<button class="button">Login</button>
				<button class="button">Sign Up</button>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
	<footer>
		<div class="footer-container">
			<div class="footer-left">
				<img src="/images/logo.png" alt="logo" class="logo" />
			</div>
			<div class="footer-right">
				<p class="company-name">Company Name</p>
				<p>Mobile: +1234567890</p>
				<p>Email: company@example.com</p>
				<p>Address: 123, Street Name, City, Country</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>
	<script src="/JS/index.js"></script>
</body>
